[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0220","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0676","title":"Sun Solaris 2.6 sdtcm_convert 本地符号链接文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 系统中的 sdtcm_convert 工具在处理临时文件时未进行充分的路径安全检查，存在符号链接（symlink）竞争条件漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建恶意的符号链接，诱使 sdtcm_convert 以特权进程身份覆写任意系统文件，从而导致敏感文件被破坏、权限提升或系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户账户权限，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0676"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.510","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00151 提供的 Solaris 2.6 官方补丁：SPARC 平台安装 105868-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105868-24），x86 平台安装 105869-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105869-21）。由于 Solaris 2.6 已终止技术支持（EOL），强烈建议升级至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.x 或更高版本以获取持续安全更新。如无法立即打补丁或升级，可临时移除 sdtcm_convert 的 setuid 权限（`chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/sdtcm_convert`）并确保 /tmp 等临时目录设置 sticky bit，限制非授权本地用户的 CDE 工具集访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/575","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19990809134220.A1191%40hades.chaoz.org","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0676","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0676.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5088ae3b-1fe3-4296-b335-fed943d90602.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0219","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0093","title":"IBM AIX nslookup 命令本地权限提升漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统自带的 nslookup 命令在执行过程中未能正确清除提升的特权，导致本地普通用户可通过调用该命令获得 root 权限。攻击者只需拥有系统本地访问权限即可利用此漏洞，无需身份认证或用户交互。该漏洞影响多个 AIX 发行版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级 AIX 操作系统至厂商已修复的最新版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0093"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.180","remediation":"建议立即安装 IBM 针对此漏洞发布的 APAR 补丁（IX73355），将 bos.net.tcp.client 文件集更新至 4.3.2.0 或更高版本。临时缓解措施可移除 nslookup 命令的 setuid root 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/nslookup。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0093"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0219.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0217","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0092","title":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 portmir 本地缓冲区溢出与不安全的临时文件创建漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.2.1 系统中的 /usr/bin/portmir 命令存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞，攻击者可通过向该命令传递特制超长参数触发栈溢出，覆盖返回地址以执行任意代码；同时该命令还存在不安全的临时文件创建问题，攻击者可利用符号链接竞争条件劫持临时文件实现提权。本地攻击者在拥有普通用户权限的条件下即可利用此漏洞获得 root 权限，影响 IBM AIX 4.2.1 及更早版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0092"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1997-10-29T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:34.030","remediation":"立即升级至 IBM AIX 5.1 及以上受支持版本，该问题已在后续版本中得到修复。如无法升级，以 root 执行 chmod 0755 /usr/bin/portmir 去除 setuid 位，并移除其他用户执行权限：chown root:system /usr/bin/portmir；同时在 /etc/security/sysck.cfg 中移除 portmir 条目标记。临时缓解措施可将需要 portmir 功能的用户加入专用组，通过 sudo 授权最小权限使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0092","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19306","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5917e2b15694e167c1fd9ad85775b2bdfc5fe29c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0092","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0092.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x/GHSA-673v-6c89-8w4x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0092.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4be848c8-03f3-452a-a9ce-ef9613324759.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0217.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0216","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0674","title":"BSD 系列操作系统 profil 系统调用本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统 profil(2) 系统调用存在安全缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 profile 与 execve 的组合调用，在程序执行过程中修改其内部数据空间，进而导致进程行为异常或权限提升。此漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.4、OpenBSD 2.5 及 Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 类操作系统，攻击者需具备本地用户账户权限才能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0674"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.237","remediation":"NetBSD 用户应升级至 1.4.1 及以上版本，OpenBSD 用户应升级至 2.6 及以上版本，Solaris 用户应安装对应操作系统补丁包或升级至 Solaris 8/9，以修复 profil(2) 系统调用中关于 profiling 与 execve 的内部数据空间修改问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-067.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/570","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19447","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0674","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0674.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0214","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0091","title":"IBM AIX writesrv 命令缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 操作系统中的 writesrv 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向该命令提交特制的输入参数触发溢出，覆盖内存中的关键数据结构以获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 多个版本，危害等级高，利用前提是攻击者具有本地系统访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0091"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-28T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.873","remediation":"安装 IBM AIX APAR IX68518 补丁或升级至 AIX 4.3.3 及以上维护级别。如无法立即打补丁，可移除 writesrv 命令的 setuid root 权限执行 `chmod 0500 /usr/sbin/writesrv`，或通过文件权限控制限制非 root 用户执行该命令作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0091"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0214.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0213","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0090","title":"IBM AIX rcp 命令本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"AIX 系统 rcp 命令存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 rcp 命令提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而覆盖内存数据并获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 IBM AIX 操作系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。利用需要本地用户身份，成功利用后攻击者可完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0090"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1997-10-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.733","remediation":"IBM 已在 AIX 4.x 版本的 APAR IY09308 中修复此漏洞，建议更新 bos.rte.net_filesystem fileset 至包含该 APAR 的维护级别。临时缓解措施可移除 /usr/bin/rcp 的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /usr/bin/rcp，或禁用 r-commands 服务（rshd、rexecd）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0090"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0213.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0672","title":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端 Topic 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端在处理 IRC 频道主题（Topic）时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向运行该客户端的用户发送特制的畸形频道主题数据，触发缓冲区溢出，导致客户端崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 版本，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0672"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.990","remediation":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 已停止维护，官方未发布修复版本。建议立即停止使用该客户端，迁移至仍在维护的 IRC 客户端（如 mIRC、HexChat、Irssi）。作为临时缓解措施，可在 IRC 服务器端或客户端配置中过滤/禁用自动解析频道主题，避免触发缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/573","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0672","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0672.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/307.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.223","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0209","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0209.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0490","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer MSHTML 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 中的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可在恶意网页中构造 IMG SRC 标签指向本地文件路径（如 file:///C:/boot.ini），当用户使用 IE 浏览器访问该页面时，浏览器会尝试加载指定本地文件，攻击者通过观察加载返回结果可判断目标文件是否存在，从而探测用户本地敏感文件信息。该漏洞利用方式简单，无需额外交互或认证，影响所有安装 IE 5.0 的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0490"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.493","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 5.01 或更高版本即可修复此漏洞。由于 IE 5.0 已停止支持多年，强烈建议升级到 Microsoft Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器，并在系统层面禁用 IE 作为 ActiveX 控件的默认处理程序以彻底规避风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0209.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0208","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0489","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.0 文件上传控件脚本粘贴漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 5.0 的 MSHTML.DLL 组件存在未信任脚本粘贴漏洞（untrusted scripted paste）。远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页，利用脚本将任意文件名粘贴至文件上传内置控件中，绕过用户交互限制，实现恶意文件的上传操作。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统上运行的 IE 5.0 浏览器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。Microsoft 已在 MS98-013 安全公告中提供修复措施。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0489"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-05-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.367","remediation":"建议升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 以上版本，微软已在 MS98-013 公告中修复该问题。当前所有受支持 Windows 版本均已内置更新版 IE，建议用户升级至现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）以避免此漏洞。如无法升级，可在 IE 安全设置中将「Internet 区域」的「对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化并执行脚本」设为「禁用」以降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-015"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0208.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0207","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0088","title":"IRIX 和 AIX automountd 服务远程代码执行漏洞","description":"IRIX 和 AIX 系统中的 automountd（autofsd）服务存在远程命令执行漏洞。攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统的该服务发送特制请求，利用服务对输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，以 root 权限执行任意命令，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，影响 IRIX 及 AIX 操作系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0088"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-10-26T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.370","remediation":"在 AIX 系统上执行 `stopsrc -g automountd` 禁用自动挂载服务，编辑 `/etc/rc.autofs` 注释自动启动项；在 IRIX 系统上执行 `/etc/init.d/autofs stop` 并删除 rc 链接。同时使用防火墙规则过滤 TCP/UDP 6969 端口，限制对 automountd 服务的网络访问。建议将老旧 IRIX/AIX 系统迁移至受支持版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www-1.ibm.com/services/brs/brspwhub.nsf/advisories/852567CC004F9038852566BF007B6393/%24file/ERS-SVA-E01-1998_004_1.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0207.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0206","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0206.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0488","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 跨框架脚本执行漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 4.0 及 5.0 版本存在跨框架安全上下文绕过漏洞（Cross-Frame 漏洞变种）。远程攻击者可通过构造恶意 URL 诱使目标用户访问，从而在不同安全区域中执行任意脚本代码，导致敏感信息泄露、会话劫持等危害。该漏洞影响所有使用受影响版本 IE 的 Windows 系统，攻击者仅需诱导用户点击恶意链接即可利用，无需身份认证。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0488"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-04-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.247","remediation":"建议立即升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 以上版本，该漏洞已在 MS99-012 安全公告中修复。如无法升级，可禁用 Active Scripting 功能作为临时缓解措施（Internet 选项 → 安全 → 自定义级别 → 脚本 → 禁用）。长期方案建议迁移至 Edge 或 Chrome 等现代浏览器。IE 6.0 及以上版本已修复此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-012"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0206.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0205","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0087","title":"IBM AIX Telnet 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"IBM AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本 Telnet 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可通过向目标系统发送特制的 Telnet 协议数据包，触发服务进程异常崩溃，导致系统完全冻结，合法用户无法登录或访问服务器资源。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1/4.2/4.3 版本，攻击门槛低，危害中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0087"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1998-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 4.3.3 或更高版本，IBM 已在后续维护版本中修复此问题。如无法升级，可在 inetd.conf 中注释 telnet 行并使用 refresh -s inetd 生效，改用 SSH 替代 telnet 服务，同时在防火墙上限制对 23/TCP 端口的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0087","https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-1999-0087","http://www.osvdb.org/7992"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0205.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0671","title":"ToxSoft NextFTP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令触发该漏洞，导致目标系统上的 NextFTP 客户端程序崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 NextFTP 1.82 版本，攻击者需诱骗用户连接至恶意 FTP 服务器，利用难度中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0671"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.857","remediation":"ToxSoft 已停止运营，官方未发布补丁。建议立即停止使用 NextFTP 1.82，迁移至仍受维护的 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla、WinSCP）。如暂时无法替换，可通过网络防火墙或 IPS 规则拦截包含超长 CWD 命令的 FTP 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/572","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19448","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0671","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0671.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/308.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.224","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0203","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0086","title":"IBM AIX routed 远程敏感文件修改漏洞","description":"AIX 系统中的 routed 路由守护进程存在访问控制缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向目标系统发送特制的 RIP 路由协议报文，利用该漏洞可修改系统敏感文件，从而获得非授权访问权限或造成系统配置被篡改。该漏洞影响 AIX 操作系统的 routed 服务，攻击者可通过伪造路由更新实施攻击。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0086"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-01-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:32.940","remediation":"升级 AIX 至受支持的最新版本（7.2 TL5/7.3 及以上），该版本已不再使用存在漏洞的 routed 实现。若无法升级，立即停止 routed 服务（`stopsrc -s routed`）并在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释相关行，同时在防火墙侧阻断外部对 UDP 520 端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0086"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0203.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0202","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0670","title":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Eyedog ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过构造特制网页诱使用户访问，触发缓冲区溢出从而执行任意命令。该漏洞影响了 Internet Explorer 浏览器中集成的 Eyedog ActiveX 控件，攻击者需要诱导用户打开恶意网页或包含恶意内容的电子邮件才能成功利用，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0670"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.737","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 于 1999 年 8 月发布的安全公告 MS99-032 对应补丁（KB240308），或通过 Windows Update 更新至最新版本的 Internet Explorer。该补丁为 Eyedog ActiveX 控件设置 kill bit，阻止其在 IE 中加载。作为手动缓解措施，可在注册表 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下为 CLSID {A5ECB622-137C-11D2-B34D-00C04FB6F6E1} 创建 Compatibility Flags 值为 0x400 的 DWORD 项，同样可禁用该控件。长远建议升级至现代操作系统及浏览器，因较新版本已不再包含此控件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/j-064.shtml","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-032","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0670","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0670.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/25a429f7c036c8b0416069b51c2af695a6b890c2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4/GHSA-vw7j-x4wv-gff4.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0670.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88352/info.html","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0202.toml"}]